17.5 Reporting claims
:SKRSLUT.
.br
On returning home, a claim report is to be submitted to
Privatsikring. In order to ensure correct processing of the
case, all relevant documents must be enclosed, including
information about any corresponding insurance policies taken
out with a different company. The insured is obliged to
present documentation such as unused airline tickets, receipts
and itineraries (all as original documents).
.sp 5mm
.kp off
It is a condition that the late arrival of the insured is not caused by
the insured having failed to allow sufficient time for transport.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED
17.2 Exceptions
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance does not cover late arrival after the time when the insured
arrived in the departure hall.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
17.3 Coverage - Rejoining the route in the event of delays to a connecting
flight.
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers expenses up to DKK 10,000 per person for new airline
tickets (max. economy class) and DKK 1,000 per person per day for hotel
accommodation and meals on account of late arrival for a reserved
connecting flight.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
17.3.1 Acceptable reasons for the insured failing to arrive on time for
his/her connecting flight are:
.of 5mm
*¤the insured, through no fault of his/her own, failing to arrive on time
for the connecting flight and there being no alternative flight available
.of 5mm
*¤unexpected weather conditions, natural disasters or technical grounds.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
17.3.2 If the insured is unable to check his/her baggage all the way
to his/her final destination according to the itinerary, the insured
must make sure to comply with the official check-in times for
physically changing flights at the airport(s) in question in order to
be eligible for insurance cover.
.kp off
.kp on
.sp 3mm
17.3.3 If the insured is able to check his/her baggage all the way to
his/her final destination according to the itinerary, the insured must
make sure to comply with the official transfer times for physically
changing flights at the airport(s) in question in order to be eligible
for insurance cover.
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
