17.1 Coverage - Late arrival in connection with transport to the
departure hall.
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance provides coverage for reasonable and necessary extra
expenses up to DKK 10,000 per person for transport - max. economy class
- and DKK 1,000 per person per day for hotel accommodation and meals:
.of 5mm
* when the insured has started the journey from his/her residence/place of
accommodation, or from the holiday residence and, through no fault of
his/her own is unavoidably prevented from reaching the departure hall in
accordance with his/her itinerary.
.sp 3mm
